WEBVTT

00:00:30.712 --> 00:00:34.742
So by now, my talk is already 6,000 words long,

00:00:34.742 --> 00:00:36.890
and I feel like I should stop here.

00:00:36.890 --> 00:00:39.310
(Laughter)

00:00:39.310 --> 00:00:41.131
At the same time, I probably owe you

00:00:41.131 --> 00:00:42.137
some explanation

00:00:42.137 --> 00:00:45.240
about the images that you just saw.

00:00:45.240 --> 00:00:47.963
What I am trying to do as a photographer,

00:00:47.963 --> 00:00:50.446
as an artist, is to bring the world

00:00:50.446 --> 00:00:53.823
of art and science together.

00:00:53.823 --> 00:00:56.162
Whether it is an image of a soap bubble

00:00:56.162 --> 00:00:58.928
captured at the very moment where it's bursting,

00:00:58.928 --> 00:01:01.400
as you can see in this image,